import re

def extract_function_signature(code_snippet):
    function_name = re.search('def\\s+(\\w+)\\(', code_snippet).group(2)
    input_params = re.search('\\((.*?)\\)', code_snippet).group(1)
    return_type = input_params.split(',')[-1].strip()
    additional_info = code_snippet.split('(')[1].split(')')[0]
    return {'Name': function_name, 'Input Parameter(s)': input_params, 'Return Type': return_type, 'Additional Information': additional_info}
